sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Platform
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as MLflow Operator<br/>controller-runtime
    participant HelmEngine as Helm Renderer<br/>(in-process library)
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MigJob as Migration Job<br/>(Alembic Python)

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: MLflow CR Reconciliation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create/Update MLflow CR<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (informer)<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Discovery API check<br/>(HTTPRoute, ConsoleLink, ServiceMonitor CRDs)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Available CRDs
    Operator->>HelmEngine: Render chart with CRD spec → Helm values
    HelmEngine-->>Operator: Rendered K8s objects
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply (SSA)<br/>fieldOwner: mlflow-operator
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Applied resources

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Client Request to MLflow
    User->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/...<br/>HTTPS, Bearer Token
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward via HTTPRoute<br/>8443/TCP, TLS (service-ca)
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>User's Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Allow/Deny
    alt Authorized
        MLflow->>PG: Query/Store metadata<br/>5432/TCP, TLS optional
        PG-->>MLflow: Result
        MLflow->>S3: Store/Retrieve artifacts<br/>443/TCP, AWS credentials
        S3-->>MLflow: Artifact data
        MLflow-->>Gateway: JSON Response
        Gateway-->>User: 200 OK
    else Denied
        MLflow-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
        Gateway-->>User: 403 Forbidden
    end

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Database Migration (on version upgrade)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Scale MLflow Deployment to 0<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Scaled down
    Operator->>Operator: Wait for all pods terminated
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Migration Job<br/>(same image, volumes, env)
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Job created
    MigJob->>PG: Run Alembic migration<br/>5432/TCP, TLS optional
    PG-->>MigJob: Migration result
    alt Success
        MigJob-->>K8sAPI: Job completed (exit 0)
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Job success event
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Restore Deployment replicas<br/>Update status.version
    else Terminal Failure
        MigJob-->>K8sAPI: Job failed (exit 2/3)
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Job failure event
        Operator->>Operator: Set error condition<br/>(no retry)
    else Retryable Failure
        MigJob-->>K8sAPI: Job failed (exit 1)
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Job failure event
        Operator->>Operator: Retry after 2min delay
    end
